Package hu.bme.mit.theta.core.type.booltype

Bool type and its expressions. Use BoolExprs to create them. - BoolType: the actual Boolean type - TrueExpr: true literal - FalseExpr: false literal - NotExpr: negation - AndExpr: and (conjunction) - OrExpr: or (disjunction) - ImplyExpr: implication - XorExpr: exclusive or (xor) - IffExpr: equivalence (if and only if) - ExistsExpr: existential quantifier - ForallExpr: universal quantifier
